system requirement:
    - php version >= 7.4
    - mysql
    - apache or nginx (requires nginx)
how to install
    1. clone project from github
    2. create data base
    3. cd to path/folder-code and run composer update (if php version < 7.4, application will error)
    4. copy .env-example and run command php artisan key:generate
        4.1 install ckfinder by command php artisan ckfinder:download
        4.2 make folder directory structure
            storage
                app
                framework
                    cache
                    sessions
                    views
                logs

    5. clear all cache and optimize by command
        php artisan cache:clear
        php artisan optimize


